2014-09-29 version 0.4.4:

  * Fix log level when accept is failed
  * Show detailed error message when accept failed

2014-07-22 version 0.4.3:

  * Fixed Makefile for test (#10).
  * Stopped using -O4 (#11).
  * Added -pthread to compilation option (#12).
  * Added remove_session function to session_pool (#14).

2013-06-21 version 0.4.2:

  * Added disabling session timeout feature
  * Added a virtual destructor to msgpack::rpc::dispatcher

2013-03-15 version 0.4.1:

  * Add session::close()/open() feature
  * Add configurable session-pool expire time and limit size

2013-02-15 version 0.4.0-p1:

  * Fix configure.in for clang with -O4 option
  * Update autoconf script for distribution, exclude mplex sources

2013-01-11 version 0.4.0

  * Forked from msgpack-rpc
  * Eliminated zlib dependency
  * Renamed directory msgpack-rpc -> jubatus/msgpack-rpc
  * Renamed libmsgpack-rpc -> libjubatus_msgpack-rpc
  * Add request cancellation feature
  * Add server timeout feature

2011-02-20 version 0.3.1

  * session_pool keeps released connection upto 60 seconds

2010-08-16 version 0.3.0

  * increments library's version-info
  * fixes circular reference problem of shared_ptr
  * adds high-load test cases
  * graceful shutting down of timer threads
  * fixes race condition of shared_zone->allocate
  * increases default buffer size

2010-08-10 version 0.2.0

  * underlying transport layer is redesigned
  * supports UDP
  * supports UNIX socket
  * address class is redesigned
  * adds session::call_apply and session::notify_apply methods
  * bug fix: inserts a future in reqtable before sending data

2010-05-07 version 0.1.0

  * first release

